<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: PV-8 "Zyklop" frame -->
  <DMS_Apparel_PV8_Core.label>PV-8「単眼」機体</DMS_Apparel_PV8_Core.label>
  <!-- EN: A heavy armed powerarmour or so-called "Dragoon" used by the Colonial Army task force. This is probably the largest piece of infantry equipments deployed by the colonial fleet on surface of this planet. The extremely thick armor and powerful power system enable the ground garrison to maintain sufficient mobile firepower to deal with interference in the colonization project. -->
  <DMS_Apparel_PV8_Core.description>植民軍機動部隊が使用する重武装強化装甲、いわゆる「龍機」。これはおそらく植民艦隊がこの惑星表面に展開した最大の歩兵装備です。極めて厚い装甲と強力な動力系統により、地上駐屯軍は植民計画への妨害に対処するのに十分な機動火力を維持できます。</DMS_Apparel_PV8_Core.description>
  <!-- EN: mechanical fist -->
  <DMS_Apparel_PV8_Core.tools.mechanical_fist.label>機械拳</DMS_Apparel_PV8_Core.tools.mechanical_fist.label>
  <!-- EN: mechanical leg -->
  <DMS_Apparel_PV8_Core.tools.mechanical_leg.label>機械脚</DMS_Apparel_PV8_Core.tools.mechanical_leg.label>
  
  <!-- EN: PV-8 "Zyklop" helmet -->
  <DMS_Apparel_PV8_Helmet.label>PV-8「単眼」頭部装甲</DMS_Apparel_PV8_Helmet.label>
  <!-- EN: A heavy-duty helmet that uses small optical probes arranged in a distributed manner as sensors in order to prevent damage from frontal hits from large-caliber weapons. -->
  <DMS_Apparel_PV8_Helmet.description>大口径兵器の正面攻撃による損傷を防ぐため、分散配置された小型光学探査装置を感知器として使用する頑丈な頭部装甲。</DMS_Apparel_PV8_Helmet.description>
  
  <!-- EN: PV-8 "Zyklop" frame module -->
  <DMS_Module_PV8_Core.label>PV-8「単眼」機体兵装</DMS_Module_PV8_Core.label>
  <!-- EN: These heavy armed powerarmour or so-called "Dragoon" used by the Colonial Army task force. Probably the largest piece of infantry equipments deployed by the colonial fleet on surface of this planet. Their extremely thick armor and powerful power system allowing ground garrison to maintain sufficient mobile firepower to deal with interference in the colonization. -->
  <DMS_Module_PV8_Core.description>植民軍機動部隊が使用するこれらの重武装強化装甲、いわゆる「龍機」。おそらく植民艦隊がこの惑星表面に展開した最大の歩兵装備です。その極めて厚い装甲と強力な動力系統により、地上駐屯軍は植民化への妨害に対処するのに十分な機動火力を維持できます。</DMS_Module_PV8_Core.description>
  
  <!-- EN: PV-8 "Zyklop" helmet -->
  <DMS_Module_PV8_Helmet.label>PV-8「単眼」頭部装甲</DMS_Module_PV8_Helmet.label>
  <!-- EN: A heavy-duty helmet that uses small optical probes arranged in a distributed manner as sensors in order to prevent damage from frontal hits from large-caliber weapons. -->
